does not have the little Reminder Window when you exit it, and is registered
in your name. Registered users will be the first to be notified, through the
electronic mail of upcoming updates of the program. They may @{" upgrade " link Update} their
version at a nominal cost.  At the end of this chapter you will find a form.
Please complete it and sent it in if you wish to register the program.  Read
on for information on the registration fee.

